<plot>Laura is just like any other single young woman her age, apart from the fact that most single young women don't kill and dissect the men that they date. 'Next Victim' is a short black-comedy told through the eyes of Laura Hargraves as she reflects on the lessons she's learnt in her transformation from naive young girl with a curiosity for killing into a confident young woman with an effective and efficient murder regime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?394744</url></doc>
